dc_title_s: Pacific Ocean, Archipiélago de Colón (Galapagos Islands), Ecuador, Isla Santa María and approaches (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Ecuadorean and U.S. charts to 1991." Place names in Spanish with glossary in English. "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram and tidal information. Map No.22526 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
